		<title>Fighting COVID-19 with facts and figures</title>
		<link>https://miningnews.co.za/2020/07/15/fighting-covid-19-with-facts-and-figures/</link>
					<comments>https://miningnews.co.za/2020/07/15/fighting-covid-19-with-facts-and-figures/#respond</comments>
		
